parameters:
Phew... I've tidied up quite a bit... Oh? Already,
it's this late.

There might be someone who wants a massage before
going to bed soon...

Hotel Staff: Good job, we have a request for a
massage. Please go to room 502.

Hotel Staff: Before that, let me explain a few
things about the job.

Hotel Staff: Our hotel's massages don't have any
specific procedures or content.

Hotel Staff: For example, if the customer is
concerned about their shoulders, you can focus on
massaging their shoulders. And if their feet are
swollen, it's fine to spend the entire time just
massaging their feet.

Hotel Staff: There are also those who just want
someone to talk to. In that case, it's enough to
just listen to their story.

So... it means being flexible and adapting to the
customer's needs, right?

Hotel Staff: Yes, that's correct. Our main goal is
to heal the customers, so we leave the actual
content of the service up to you.

Hotel Staff: In addition, we have a system for
requesting specific staff members. If you receive
a high number of requests per month, we will give
you an additional hourly wage increase, so please
do your best.

If I might get a raise, it's motivating. And if I
receive lots of gratitude, my popularity might
increase too...
